WEBVTT

00:01.700 --> 00:04.110
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:05.954 --> 00:08.089
Well, here are the
proud parents-to-be.

00:08.157 --> 00:09.991
Yes, and we've been shopping.

00:09.992 --> 00:11.943
Yeah, look what we found.
Pretty neat, huh?

00:11.943 --> 00:13.428
Oh that's perfect.

00:13.429 --> 00:15.730
It'll do wonders for his motor
skills and his mental acuity.

00:15.731 --> 00:18.383
Oh, yeah. Check this out, we
got one for the baby, too.

00:19.852 --> 00:23.588
Our next city councilman,
ladies and gentlemen!

00:23.589 --> 00:26.357
Boy, it's gonna be tough finding
a replacement for you, Woody.

00:26.358 --> 00:28.126
Well, why would you want
to replace me, Sam?

00:28.127 --> 00:29.594
Well, you can't tend bar here

00:29.661 --> 00:31.496
and be a councilman
at the same time.

00:31.564 --> 00:32.762
That's a full-time job.

00:32.831 --> 00:34.415
It is, Sam?
Yeah.

00:34.483 --> 00:37.619
And working here at Cheers
is a full-time job, too.

00:37.687 --> 00:39.253
It is, Sam?

00:39.321 --> 00:41.189
Yes.

00:41.190 --> 00:43.274
Well, can't I tend bar
at least sometimes?

00:43.275 --> 00:46.711
I mean, what all does a city
councilman have to do anyway?

00:46.712 --> 00:48.229
Well, Woody, our present
councilman, Kevin Fogerty,

00:48.230 --> 00:50.532
rises at the crack of dawn,
6:30 to be exact.

00:50.599 --> 00:53.234
Then he showers,
shaves, goes downstairs

00:53.235 --> 00:55.436
for a leisurely breakfast
with his wife Estelle.

00:55.437 --> 00:57.271
Then he takes his son
Joseph, eight,

00:57.272 --> 01:00.392
and Hillary, 11, to the
Fenwick Elementary School.

01:00.459 --> 01:02.260
At least that was his routine

01:02.328 --> 01:06.398
before, the court order
deprived me of my right to know.

01:07.649 --> 01:10.818
Big Brother, my friends,
Big Brother!

01:12.037 --> 01:14.055
Years from now,
they're gonna ask me

01:14.123 --> 01:16.258
why I didn't see the signs.

01:18.895 --> 01:20.745
(theme song begins)

01:22.932 --> 01:25.183
♪ Sometimes you want to go ♪

01:25.250 --> 01:28.753
♪ Where everybody
knows your name ♪

01:30.690 --> 01:34.793
♪ And they're always
glad you came ♪

01:34.861 --> 01:37.896
♪ You wanna be
where you can see ♪

01:37.964 --> 01:40.231
♪ Our troubles
are all the same ♪

01:40.299 --> 01:45.303
♪ You wanna go where
everybody knows your name. ♪

